- if user_signed_in?
  = form_with(model: [@event, @comment], local: true, class: "comment-form", id: "js-comment-form") do |f|
    = f.label :comment, "コメント", class: "comment-label"
    = f.text_area :comment, class: "comment-area"
    = f.submit "送信", class: "comment-btn"
- else
  コメントの投稿にはログインが必要です